#!/usr/bin/env bash

notify-send -t 30000 --icon="/usr/share/icons/Papirus/24x24/status/dialog-error.svg" "WARNING!

You are about to edit the .jwmrc file
that is specific to this theme. The 
theme's name is on line 4 of the .jwmrc
file.

When you have finished editing the file, 
copy and paste the .jwmrc file from your 
Home folder into its appropriate theme 
folder located in...

 ~/.config/jwm/

...or your changes won't carry over
if you change JWM Themes again.
"
